<p>And the last one is killer</p></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_MiniToolbox"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:68493920,&quot;threadId&quot;:&quot;3531720&quot;,&quot;contentId&quot;:&quot;13052863&quot;,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;nextmsnbcstar&quot;}"></div><ul class="list"><li class="box votes"><div class="label">1 vote</div></li></ul></div><span class="commentdate"><a href="#c68493920" title="Link to this comment">#1.1</a> - Tue Jul 31, 2012 8:22 PM EDT</span></div></div></div><div class="vine-p p-comment_Comment showAvatars commentbody child " id="c68496147"><div class="printerData hide" data-printer="{&quot;commentId&quot;:68496147,&quot;authorDomain&quot;:&quot;patp11111&quot;,&quot;authorDisplayName&quot;:&quot;Pat P11111&quot;}"></div><div class="c_author"><div class="normal"><a href="http://patp11111.newsvine.com/"><img class="comment_author_avatar" src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/_/blank.gif" data-avatar_src="http://www.cdn.newsvine.com/_vine/images/av/60x60/msnbc.jpg" width="35" height="35" alt="Comment author avatar" data-is_default_avatar="true" /></a><a href="http://patp11111.newsvine.com/">Pat P11111</a></div></div><div id="commentText_68496147" class="c_text"><div class="normal"><div class="commentSource"><p>India is really at the front of developing off the grid solar for the undeveloped parts of the country, quite a bit of it actually.</p>
